WEBVTT

00:06.756 --> 00:09.342
<i>Previously on</i> <i>American Rust...</i>

00:09.384 --> 00:10.760
<i>Fifty-one percent
of your employees</i>

00:10.802 --> 00:12.679
<i>would like to be
represented by a union.</i>

00:12.721 --> 00:13.930
<i>It's what the cards say.</i>

00:14.014 --> 00:15.140
<i>Someone took a bat to
the taillights.</i>

00:15.181 --> 00:16.307
<i>Who did it?</i>

00:16.391 --> 00:17.600
<i>Gelsey, probably.</i>

00:17.642 --> 00:18.685
<i>Fentanyl.</i>

00:18.768 --> 00:19.769
<i>This is strong stuff.</i>

00:19.853 --> 00:20.812
<i>You ever fill a script for it?</i>

00:20.854 --> 00:22.147
<i>I mean, not in a long time.</i>

00:22.188 --> 00:24.232
<i>You mind my asking
where you get this filled?</i>

00:24.315 --> 00:26.109
<i>-Jackson's.
- Jackson.</i>

00:26.151 --> 00:28.069
<i>[Steve]</i> <i>The guy with Novick
was his dealer?</i>

00:28.153 --> 00:30.113
<i>But are you hunting him down
because he's dealing,</i>

00:30.155 --> 00:31.614
<i>or because
it might help Grace's son?</i>

00:31.656 --> 00:34.784
<i>If you'd rather I left you
out of this going forward,</i>

00:34.826 --> 00:35.910
<i>I get it, no hard feelings.</i>

00:35.994 --> 00:37.078
<i>I work for you, Chief.</i>

00:37.162 --> 00:38.538
<i>You understand
I've been appointed</i>

00:38.580 --> 00:39.706
<i>to serve as your lawyer?</i>

00:39.789 --> 00:40.790
<i>I don't want a lawyer.</i>

00:40.832 --> 00:42.042
<i>I can work to help your brother,</i>

00:42.083 --> 00:44.544
<i>or I can work to help
your friend, Mr. Poe.</i>

00:44.586 --> 00:45.962
<i>But I can't do both.</i>

00:46.046 --> 00:47.964
<i>If I help one,
it might mean harming the other.</i>

00:48.048 --> 00:50.717
<i>[Lee]</i> <i>I care for you.
I'm scared for you.</i>

00:50.759 --> 00:51.968
<i>Bail is denied.</i>

00:52.052 --> 00:53.511
<i>[Harris]</i> <i>You could be headed
to Farmington.</i>

00:53.595 --> 00:55.055
<i>-Felonies make up a big chunk</i>

00:55.138 --> 00:56.306
<i>of the population,</i>

00:56.389 --> 00:58.224
<i>-so keep your head down.
Hey, pretty boy.</i>

00:58.308 --> 00:59.684
<i>You gave me your word!</i>

00:59.726 --> 01:00.977
<i>Come on, Chuck.</i>

01:01.061 --> 01:05.273
<i>Goddamn it! Fuck.</i>

01:11.946 --> 01:14.532
<i>What happened to you?</i>

01:29.089 --> 01:32.092
<i>atmospheric music</i>

01:39.808 --> 01:43.853
<i>bluesy guitar music</i>

02:54.507 --> 02:56.801
<i>suspenseful music</i>

03:30.877 --> 03:33.963
<i>It's you. My man.</i>

03:49.771 --> 03:51.606
Can you give me
the names of anyone

03:51.648 --> 03:54.067
<i>who might have a grudge
against you or your son?</i>

03:54.150 --> 03:58.071
<i>Everyone in this frickin' town
has a grudge against me.</i>

04:02.450 --> 04:04.953
<i>Pam Novick, obviously.</i>

04:04.994 --> 04:06.120
<i>My boss, Gelsey.</i>

04:06.204 --> 04:07.288
<i>He's the most likely.</i>

04:07.330 --> 04:09.207
<i>That cunt of a D.A.,
Sue Herlitz.</i>

04:09.249 --> 04:11.251
<i>Judge Paronne obviously
has it in for Billy.</i>

04:11.334 --> 04:13.628
<i>I don't really think the judge
would want to firebomb your car.</i>

04:13.670 --> 04:16.422
<i>I didn't really think anybody
would want to firebomb my car</i>

04:16.464 --> 04:18.049
<i>-until they did it last night.
Okay.</i>

04:18.091 --> 04:22.178
<i>Okay. Uh, sir,
maybe let me do this for now.</i>

04:22.262 --> 04:24.514
<i>contemplative music</i>

04:24.597 --> 04:27.558
<i>What about, uh,
your husband, Virgil?</i>

04:27.600 --> 04:29.894
You think
one of the girlfriends...

04:40.780 --> 04:43.408
<i>I am being punished.</i>

04:44.075 --> 04:46.828
<i>I'm not sure why,
'cause I really...</i>

04:46.911 --> 04:49.038
<i>I really did the best I could.</i>

04:49.122 --> 04:51.124
<i>You've been
a good mother, Grace.</i>

04:51.165 --> 04:53.001
<i>Well, it wasn't enough.</i>

04:53.084 --> 04:54.419
<i>And I've been
calling the prison,</i>

04:54.502 --> 04:56.504
<i>and they say it takes a week
to process me</i>

04:56.546 --> 04:58.256
<i>to put me
on the-the visitors' list.</i>

04:58.339 --> 05:00.216
<i>Is there nothing you can do
to speed that up?</i>

05:00.258 --> 05:04.429
<i>Well, if there was,
I hope you know that I'd do it.</i>

05:05.096 --> 05:08.808
<i>Who is this guy...
lying about Billy?</i>

05:08.891 --> 05:10.101
<i>Saying he killed Pete?</i>

05:10.184 --> 05:11.269
<i>Pete Novick was a junkie.</i>

05:11.352 --> 05:13.271
<i>-Is this guy a junkie, too?
- I don't know.</i>

05:13.313 --> 05:16.232
<i>Well, why doesn't anyone
know anything about him?</i>

05:16.316 --> 05:17.483
<i>I've been trying.</i>

05:17.525 --> 05:19.402
<i>I need your help, Del.
Please try to help me.</i>

05:19.485 --> 05:20.528
<i>They shut me out!</i>

05:20.570 --> 05:24.657
<i>I-I got no leads
to work on my own, okay?</i>

05:31.914 --> 05:35.710
<i>Did Billy say anything
about what happened at the mill?</i>

05:35.793 --> 05:38.880
<i>What makes you think
he was even there?</i>

05:39.505 --> 05:41.632
<i>I'm not saying he was
or he wasn't,</i>

05:41.674 --> 05:44.844
<i>I'm just telling you
what the D.A. is saying.</i>

05:49.015 --> 05:50.892
<i>Billy wouldn't talk to me.</i>

05:51.726 --> 05:54.479
<i>But he was spending a whole
lot of time with Lee English.</i>

05:54.520 --> 05:56.647
<i>Maybe he said something to her.</i>

05:56.731 --> 05:57.982
<i>Okay.</i>

06:04.947 --> 06:07.492
<i>What are you doing?</i>

06:39.399 --> 06:41.526
<i>This is awful.</i>

06:42.318 --> 06:44.237
<i>Why am I looking at this?</i>

06:44.320 --> 06:46.239
<i>He was my old partner.</i>

06:50.284 --> 06:52.036
<i>When did this happen?</i>

06:52.120 --> 06:54.163
<i>Night before last.</i>

06:54.205 --> 06:56.249
<i>I was there.</i>

07:05.049 --> 07:08.970
<i>Chuck asked me to be involved.</i>

07:09.053 --> 07:12.723
<i>I refused, so he did this.</i>

07:13.224 --> 07:16.144
<i>He asked for help,
and I said no.</i>

07:16.227 --> 07:18.604
<i>I was just trying
to do right by him,</i>

07:18.646 --> 07:21.482
<i>and I'm just trying
to do right by you.</i>

07:21.566 --> 07:24.068
<i>I need you to know I care,</i>

07:24.110 --> 07:26.612
<i>and I'm trying.</i>

07:29.991 --> 07:31.742
<i>I do.</i>

07:33.453 --> 07:36.122
<i>Thank you for telling me this.</i>

07:38.249 --> 07:39.750
<i>We are gonna look out
for one another,</i>

07:39.834 --> 07:43.754
<i>and nobody is gonna hurt
either of us anymore.</i>

07:45.631 --> 07:48.050
<i>We're gonna figure it all out.</i>

07:48.134 --> 07:51.012
<i>As long as we stick together.</i>

07:52.388 --> 07:53.973
<i>Okay?</i>

07:58.478 --> 08:00.813
<i>Gonna be late.</i>

08:05.276 --> 08:07.278
<i>Are you coming by after work?</i>

08:07.778 --> 08:08.738
<i>I'm looking forward to it.</i>

08:08.821 --> 08:11.199
<i>We got interrupted last night.</i>

08:13.534 --> 08:17.163
<i>somber music</i>

08:41.729 --> 08:43.481
<i>It's better this way.</i>

08:43.523 --> 08:44.941
<i>Every time he opens a door,</i>

08:45.024 --> 08:48.444
<i>every time he hears footsteps
coming around the corner...</i>

08:48.486 --> 08:50.738
<i>Laredo'll start sweating,
thinking it's me.</i>

08:50.821 --> 08:53.991
<i>His food won't sit well
the rest of his life.</i>

08:57.745 --> 08:59.622
<i>Well, all right,
but if I'm gonna be holy,</i>

08:59.664 --> 09:01.249
<i>I got to get some fun out of it.</i>

09:02.542 --> 09:04.418
<i>-[Lee Dixon]</i> <i>Well, well, well.
-[Wayne]</i> <i>Hello.</i>

09:04.460 --> 09:07.338
<i>Mr. and Mrs. Worth,
Ms. Worth, Randy McCall.</i>

09:07.421 --> 09:09.048
<i>How do you do?</i>

09:09.131 --> 09:09.799
<i>Yeah?</i>

09:09.840 --> 09:11.884
<i>It's me. Come on.</i>

09:13.344 --> 09:14.512
<i>What's up, man?</i>

09:14.554 --> 09:17.557
<i>Got me the fuck out
in the boonies.</i>

09:17.598 --> 09:19.350
<i>Come on.</i>

09:23.020 --> 09:24.105
<i>You been good?</i>

09:24.146 --> 09:28.359
<i>Yeah. I got to plan
a whole sweet 16 for Tashi.</i>

09:28.401 --> 09:33.114
<i>It's expensive as fuck,
but I can't say no.</i>

09:35.533 --> 09:37.034
<i>-The usual?
- Depends.</i>

09:37.118 --> 09:39.287
<i>You giving me a break
for what I paid in gas?</i>

09:53.050 --> 09:54.135
<i>Good, good.</i>

09:54.218 --> 09:55.678
<i>Send T my love, all right?</i>

09:55.761 --> 09:57.430
<i>Yeah. Will do.</i>

10:02.393 --> 10:04.812
<i>tense music</i>

10:04.895 --> 10:07.440
<i>Two on skinny.</i>

10:13.237 --> 10:14.655
<i>-What's up, man?
- Hey, bro.</i>

10:14.697 --> 10:15.698
<i>Thanks.</i>

10:15.781 --> 10:16.699
<i>All right, champ.</i>

10:16.741 --> 10:18.242
<i>Stay loose.</i>

10:18.284 --> 10:20.036
<i>Stay fresh.</i>

10:37.845 --> 10:40.181
<i>Thank you for your time.</i>

10:40.222 --> 10:41.599
<i>The union made their pitch.</i>

10:41.682 --> 10:45.645
<i>Now I want to make sure you
have every bit of information</i>

10:45.686 --> 10:47.813
<i>you need
to make an educated decision</i>

10:47.897 --> 10:49.649
<i>about what's best for you,</i>

10:49.690 --> 10:51.734
<i>because you
are your own best advocates.</i>

10:51.776 --> 10:53.944
<i>-You've got to be kidding me.
What happens</i>

10:54.028 --> 10:57.573
<i>when a union comes in is they
start telling you what you want.</i>

10:57.615 --> 10:59.033
<i>They have trouble listening.</i>

10:59.116 --> 11:04.205
<i>One of the first things they do
is seek money from employees.</i>

11:04.246 --> 11:06.499
<i>You've got to be kidding me.</i>

11:06.540 --> 11:08.334
<i>I'll be around
after the information session</i>

11:08.417 --> 11:09.585
<i>and happy to answer
any questions.</i>

11:09.627 --> 11:11.837
<i>Yeah, I'm sure you will be.</i>

11:14.840 --> 11:17.385
<i>What you are doing
out there is bullshit,</i>

11:17.468 --> 11:19.095
<i>but at least
that's your own space.</i>

11:19.136 --> 11:21.514
<i>I am warning you once,
and only once,</i>

11:21.555 --> 11:24.475
<i>stay off of my property.</i>

11:24.975 --> 11:26.936
<i>What on earth
are you talking about?</i>

11:26.977 --> 11:28.437
<i>You know exactly
what I'm talking about.</i>

11:28.521 --> 11:29.730
<i>Don't touch my fucking stuff.</i>

11:29.772 --> 11:31.107
<i>Don't touch my car,
don't touch my--</i>

11:31.148 --> 11:33.651
<i>Grace, I have no idea
what you mean.</i>

11:33.734 --> 11:36.028
<i>-That's bullshit!
- But you're 20 minutes late.</i>

11:36.070 --> 11:40.157
<i>So you need to step back,
go sit down in your chair</i>

11:40.199 --> 11:42.576
<i>and listen to what
this woman has to say.</i>

11:43.035 --> 11:47.832
<i>I am this close
to firing you for cause.</i>

11:47.873 --> 11:49.333
<i>Do not push me.</i>

11:49.375 --> 11:51.961
...in order to press
an issue with your employer

11:52.002 --> 11:54.547
<i>that you may not agree with.</i>

11:55.047 --> 11:57.633
<i>I want to ensure
that everyone understands</i>

11:57.717 --> 12:01.470
<i>the risks they'll be taking
if this vote were to pass.</i>

12:01.554 --> 12:03.431
<i>How much money
are you getting paid to be here?</i>

12:03.514 --> 12:04.432
<i>Excuse me?</i>

12:04.515 --> 12:05.975
<i>How much is the old man
paying you</i>

12:06.016 --> 12:07.727
<i>-to be here right now?
Grace, don't start.</i>

12:07.810 --> 12:08.894
<i>It's okay.</i>

12:08.978 --> 12:11.147
<i>I work for my money,
just like you.</i>

12:11.230 --> 12:13.357
<i>Okay. I-I just want to know
how much he's willing</i>

12:13.399 --> 12:17.778
<i>to pay you to come here and
talk us out of what we're owed.</i>

12:17.820 --> 12:20.030
<i>Mr. Gelsey has paid
good salaries in this community</i>

12:20.114 --> 12:21.699
<i>-for decades.
- And he pays you</i>

12:21.741 --> 12:25.536
<i>for an hour what he pays us,
uh, per day?</i>

12:25.619 --> 12:26.787
<i>Or maybe per week.</i>

12:26.829 --> 12:28.581
<i>Enough.</i>

12:30.541 --> 12:32.418
<i>Sit down.</i>

12:33.461 --> 12:34.670
<i>tense music</i>

12:34.754 --> 12:36.922
<i>Grace, come on.</i>

12:37.882 --> 12:39.592
<i>Let's go. Okay?</i>

12:39.633 --> 12:45.139
<i>You can sit down,
or you can walk out that door.</i>

12:47.683 --> 12:49.435
<i>Grace.</i>

13:08.871 --> 13:11.290
<i>Thank you.</i>

13:17.755 --> 13:19.298
<i>You know how</i>

13:19.340 --> 13:24.136
<i>unhappy your mom was
towards the end of our marriage.</i>

13:25.095 --> 13:28.641
<i>Even before that,
before my accident,</i>

13:28.724 --> 13:30.976
<i>we had our ups and downs.</i>

13:32.645 --> 13:35.523
<i>But we always pushed through.</i>

13:36.649 --> 13:39.735
<i>You and Alejandro...</i>

13:39.777 --> 13:42.196
<i>you're gonna figure it out.</i>

13:42.279 --> 13:43.572
<i>I can feel it.</i>

13:43.656 --> 13:47.952
<i>He'd be the fool
if you two ever split.</i>

13:49.662 --> 13:51.330
<i>Thanks, Daddy.</i>

13:56.043 --> 13:59.171
<i>I've been thinking a lot
about your brother.</i>

14:00.965 --> 14:03.634
<i>I made things tough for him.</i>

14:04.093 --> 14:06.095
<i>Maybe it's a good thing he left.</i>

14:06.178 --> 14:09.306
<i>Isaac had other reasons
to be unhappy.</i>

14:09.807 --> 14:11.934
<i>You know that,
because of who he is,</i>

14:11.976 --> 14:14.562
<i>it was hard for him
to live here, right?</i>

14:16.021 --> 14:19.483
<i>This is a hard place to stay
when you're different.</i>

14:20.025 --> 14:22.528
<i>You think he's okay?</i>

14:23.946 --> 14:25.364
<i>I hope so.</i>

14:27.867 --> 14:29.660
<i>I dream about him all the time.</i>

14:29.743 --> 14:30.953
<i>You, too?</i>

14:45.175 --> 14:47.511
<i>Did you know he was coming?</i>

14:47.553 --> 14:49.221
<i>No.</i>

14:51.599 --> 14:53.976
<i>Afternoon, you two.</i>

14:54.059 --> 14:56.687
<i>I was hoping to have a word
with you, Lee,</i>

14:56.729 --> 14:57.813
<i>if that's all right.</i>

14:57.897 --> 14:59.648
<i>You want to have a word
with my daughter,</i>

14:59.690 --> 15:01.191
<i>you can have it right here.</i>

15:01.275 --> 15:03.193
<i>You don't need to be
talking to her alone.</i>

15:03.235 --> 15:06.363
<i>Eh, didn't mean any disrespect.</i>

15:06.405 --> 15:08.073
<i>Lee?</i>

15:08.657 --> 15:09.950
<i>Go ahead.</i>

15:10.034 --> 15:11.702
<i>It's about Billy.</i>

15:12.494 --> 15:13.329
<i>Okay.</i>

15:13.370 --> 15:14.997
<i>I heard the two of you
were spending</i>

15:15.039 --> 15:18.042
<i>a good deal of time together
before he was arrested.</i>

15:18.125 --> 15:19.960
<i>You know the trouble he's in.</i>

15:20.002 --> 15:21.879
<i>Wanted to ask
if he'd talked to you</i>

15:21.921 --> 15:24.006
<i>about what might've happened
at the mill.</i>

15:24.048 --> 15:25.215
<i>Maybe he left something out</i>

15:25.257 --> 15:28.594
<i>when he spoke to me
that could help him.</i>

15:28.636 --> 15:29.595
<i>No.</i>

15:29.678 --> 15:31.597
<i>No, he didn't
leave something out?</i>

15:31.639 --> 15:34.058
<i>No, he didn't tell me anything.</i>

15:34.099 --> 15:35.768
<i>So then you probably don't know</i>

15:35.851 --> 15:37.519
<i>if anyone else
was there with him.</i>

15:37.561 --> 15:38.604
<i>How would I?</i>

15:38.687 --> 15:40.856
<i>Did you ever see him sell
or do any drugs?</i>

15:40.898 --> 15:42.816
<i>You know as well as I do</i>

15:42.900 --> 15:47.571
<i>that Billy had nothing
to do with drugs, ever.</i>

15:48.113 --> 15:51.200
<i>Right. Okay then.</i>

15:51.867 --> 15:56.664
<i>Either of you happen to hear
from Isaac recently?</i>

15:56.705 --> 15:58.082
<i>No, we have not.</i>

15:58.123 --> 16:00.876
<i>Can you remind me
exactly when he left town?</i>

16:00.918 --> 16:03.504
<i>I don't think
it's any of your business</i>

16:03.587 --> 16:04.797
<i>when my son does anything.</i>

16:04.838 --> 16:06.215
<i>And if you're suggesting</i>

16:06.256 --> 16:09.843
<i>he had something to do
with what went on at the mill,</i>

16:09.885 --> 16:11.887
<i>that's interesting,
because I heard</i>

16:11.971 --> 16:13.097
<i>you got kicked off that case.</i>

16:13.180 --> 16:15.683
<i>If you want to talk to us
about anything,</i>

16:15.766 --> 16:17.977
<i>you go and get yourself
a warrant.</i>

16:18.018 --> 16:19.311
<i>Good luck with that.</i>

16:19.395 --> 16:24.316
<i>Till then, step off my property,
leave my family alone.</i>

16:27.194 --> 16:28.529
<i>I hear you, Henry.</i>

16:28.570 --> 16:30.489
<i>Thank you for your time.</i>

16:30.531 --> 16:32.700
<i>Lee.</i>

16:45.504 --> 16:46.714
<i>Officer.</i>

16:46.797 --> 16:48.340
<i>Chief. Harris.</i>

16:48.424 --> 16:49.341
<i>Sorry.</i>

16:49.425 --> 16:51.343
<i>Right.</i>

16:51.885 --> 16:53.887
<i>Tom, come on down.</i>

16:53.971 --> 16:55.723
<i>Say hello to Chief Harris.</i>

17:01.395 --> 17:03.480
<i>Oh. Um...</i>

17:04.148 --> 17:07.192
<i>Teenagers in the neighborhood...</i>

17:13.157 --> 17:14.908
<i>How you feeling, Tom?</i>

17:14.992 --> 17:16.076
<i>All right.</i>

17:16.118 --> 17:18.328
<i>Um, kind of confused,
to tell you the truth.</i>

17:18.412 --> 17:21.290
<i>Mel says you told her
you'd put in a good word</i>

17:21.331 --> 17:22.791
<i>with child welfare if she talked</i>

17:22.875 --> 17:24.084
<i>-with you at the hospital.
- Tom. Don't.</i>

17:24.126 --> 17:26.795
<i>But we still
ain't got our kids back.</i>

17:26.837 --> 17:27.713
<i>He's upset.</i>

17:27.755 --> 17:31.675
<i>We both... We miss them is all.</i>

17:31.717 --> 17:32.968
<i>You can understand that.</i>

17:33.010 --> 17:36.346
<i>I did tell child services
that Melanie was cooperative.</i>

