- Oh, okay.</i>

36:59.008 --> 37:00.301
<i>So, you're taking the car?</i>

37:00.384 --> 37:03.054
<i>-No. What--
Uh, how about...</i>

37:03.095 --> 37:05.514
<i>How about, uh, Ella Foyer?
She here?</i>

37:05.598 --> 37:07.808
<i>Sweet Ella.
Yeah, been about eight weeks,</i>

37:07.850 --> 37:09.310
<i>but it does feel like yesterday.</i>

37:09.352 --> 37:11.938
<i>Lenny Aponte, Earl Young,
Candace Adley.</i>

37:12.021 --> 37:13.439
<i>They-they all passed, too?</i>

37:13.481 --> 37:15.191
<i>I-I been here about a year.</i>

37:15.233 --> 37:17.026
<i>They must've died
before I started,</i>

37:17.109 --> 37:18.152
<i>'cause I don't know them.</i>

37:18.194 --> 37:20.071
<i>I got one of them good memories.</i>

37:22.949 --> 37:25.076
<i>Thanks for your time.</i>

37:32.959 --> 37:34.794
<i>Hello.</i>

37:35.336 --> 37:37.213
<i>My name's LeeAnn English.</i>

37:37.296 --> 37:38.881
<i>Okay. Can I help you?</i>

37:38.923 --> 37:40.633
<i>I'm looking for paralegal work.</i>

37:40.716 --> 37:44.095
<i>I have a BA from Yale,
and I've finished a semester</i>

37:44.136 --> 37:45.680
<i>at Columbia Law School.</i>

37:45.721 --> 37:49.809
<i>I'm back at home with my family
for the time being,</i>

37:49.892 --> 37:51.018
<i>and I'd like to be useful.</i>

37:51.060 --> 37:52.353
<i>Uh, the coordinator's
out to lunch.</i>

37:52.395 --> 37:54.355
<i>-You can come back tomorrow.
- I'll wait.</i>

37:54.438 --> 37:56.565
<i>I don't mind.</i>

37:57.108 --> 37:58.150
<i>Okay, then.</i>

37:58.234 --> 38:00.569
<i>There's coffee in there.
Help yourself.</i>

38:00.653 --> 38:01.988
<i>I'm fine.</i>

38:02.071 --> 38:04.490
<i>Thank you.</i>

38:09.203 --> 38:11.038
<i>Thirty-two dead people.</i>

38:11.080 --> 38:13.582
<i>Monthly refill
for every single one.</i>

38:13.666 --> 38:16.419
<i>-Uh, yeah.
- Couple doses a day,</i>

38:16.460 --> 38:18.629
<i>we're talking
maybe 2,000 pills a month.</i>

38:18.713 --> 38:21.966
<i>Let's go handcuff
our neighborhood pharmacist.</i>

38:22.008 --> 38:23.801
<i>No.</i>

38:24.593 --> 38:27.513
<i>-Excuse me?
- If we arrest Jackson,</i>

38:27.555 --> 38:29.098
<i>whoever's on the ground selling,</i>

38:29.140 --> 38:30.599
<i>they'll hear about it,
and they'll disappear.</i>

38:30.641 --> 38:33.728
<i>But he can't continue to have
access to all those drugs.</i>

38:33.811 --> 38:36.188
<i>Jackson's a criminal,
but he's not stupid.</i>

38:36.230 --> 38:37.982
<i>I'll bet he's shut down for now.</i>

38:38.065 --> 38:39.984
<i>He knows
how many people overdosed.</i>

38:40.067 --> 38:41.360
<i>I want Trent's dealer</i>

38:41.402 --> 38:43.237
<i>and whoever sold to him.</i>

38:43.321 --> 38:46.282
<i>And I'll use Jackson to get
to this Bobby Jesus prick.</i>

38:46.365 --> 38:49.035
<i>I want them all.
Every single one.</i>

38:50.286 --> 38:52.413
<i>-Uh-huh.</i>

38:52.496 --> 38:54.707
<i>What do you mean?</i>

39:00.796 --> 39:03.007
<i>What do you mean?</i>

39:04.091 --> 39:06.218
<i>I now understand
why you want to wait.</i>

39:06.260 --> 39:07.428
<i>Do you?</i>

39:07.470 --> 39:09.972
<i>Ask me again how I got the list.</i>

39:10.014 --> 39:11.182
<i>You want to wait so you can find</i>

39:11.265 --> 39:12.433
<i>this Bobby guy
for your girlfriend.</i>

39:12.475 --> 39:14.643
<i>-You tag him with drug dealing</i>

39:14.685 --> 39:16.145
<i>and killing a high school kid,
he becomes</i>

39:16.187 --> 39:17.730
<i>a pretty terrible witness
against Billy Poe.</i>

39:17.813 --> 39:18.773
<i>Explain to me</i>

39:18.814 --> 39:21.275
<i>what's wrong with getting him
for dealing and homicide.</i>

39:21.317 --> 39:23.736
<i>It depends why you're doing it.</i>

39:23.819 --> 39:25.237
<i>You can have
two different reasons</i>

39:25.279 --> 39:26.530
<i>-for doing the right thing.
- No.</i>

39:26.572 --> 39:28.199
<i>One of them's always
the most important.</i>

39:28.282 --> 39:29.950
<i>If it's the wrong reason,</i>

39:30.034 --> 39:31.452
<i>-it corrupts everything.
- Okay.</i>

39:31.494 --> 39:33.204
<i>Thanks for the philosophy class.</i>

39:33.245 --> 39:36.040
<i>Turn on the fucking car.</i>

39:41.212 --> 39:43.714
<i>Where to, boss?</i>

39:59.522 --> 40:03.317
<i>Hey there.
I was actually gonna call you.</i>

40:03.359 --> 40:06.695
<i>Someone cut my power last night.</i>

40:06.779 --> 40:09.949
<i>I-I think they broke in
through my back door.</i>

40:10.032 --> 40:11.992
<i>Thank God we're here.</i>

40:12.076 --> 40:13.619
<i>What'd they take?</i>

40:13.661 --> 40:14.787
<i>That's the weird thing.</i>

40:14.870 --> 40:17.081
<i>I don't think
they took anything.</i>

40:17.123 --> 40:18.165
<i>Huh.</i>

40:18.207 --> 40:21.419
<i>Do I, uh,
need to, like, call it in?</i>

40:21.460 --> 40:22.670
<i>Make an official report?</i>

40:22.753 --> 40:24.547
<i>'Cause I don't mind
just telling you guys</i>

40:24.630 --> 40:26.590
<i>and having you watch out.
Save you some paperwork.</i>

40:26.632 --> 40:30.386
<i>Sure. We can run
some more patrols down this way.</i>

40:30.469 --> 40:33.347
<i>If I were you, I might put
a camera out back there.</i>

40:33.389 --> 40:37.560
<i>Then you can keep an eye
on everyone who comes and goes.</i>

40:37.601 --> 40:40.312
<i>Yeah, all right.
I might do that.</i>

40:40.354 --> 40:41.605
<i>Thanks.</i>

40:41.647 --> 40:43.357
<i>Sorry, um...</i>

40:43.441 --> 40:47.069
<i>Can I help you guys
with anything?</i>

40:47.570 --> 40:50.156
<i>Right. We're out of Narcan.</i>

40:50.197 --> 40:53.117
<i>Uh, got you. Spray or injection?</i>

40:53.200 --> 40:54.201
<i>Both.</i>

40:56.203 --> 40:58.956
<i>Are you... are you...
are you kidding?</i>

40:58.998 --> 41:03.502
<i>You're gonna have our-our town
pay for an overdose he caused?</i>

41:03.586 --> 41:05.004
<i>I heard about what happened</i>

41:05.087 --> 41:09.592
<i>with that football player.
That's-that's just terrible.</i>

41:10.342 --> 41:13.262
<i>-Put it on the PD account.
- Yeah.</i>

41:13.304 --> 41:16.974
<i>You know, it's... such a shame.</i>

41:17.016 --> 41:18.434
<i>Their only son.</i>

41:18.517 --> 41:21.979
<i>That's-that's...
That is a tragedy.</i>

41:22.813 --> 41:27.318
<i>When I see his parents,
I'll give them your condolences.</i>

41:34.450 --> 41:37.411
<i></i>

41:52.676 --> 41:55.971
<i>slow, dramatic music</i>

42:23.499 --> 42:26.168
<i>Excuse me.</i>

42:30.297 --> 42:32.091
<i>Hey!</i>

42:37.429 --> 42:39.056
<i>Hey!</i>

42:40.599 --> 42:42.434
<i>Stop it.</i>

42:42.518 --> 42:44.228
<i>Jesus.</i>

42:45.563 --> 42:47.606
<i>-Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.
- No, no, no, no, no, no, please.</i>

42:47.648 --> 42:49.066
<i>Please, don't hit me.
Please, don't hit me.</i>

42:49.108 --> 42:50.609
<i>Please, don't hit me. Please,
don't hit me.</i>

42:50.651 --> 42:51.860
<i>-Please, don't hit me.
- It's o...</i>

42:51.944 --> 42:53.320
<i>-It's okay, man.
- Please, please, don't hit me.</i>

42:53.362 --> 42:54.863
<i>Please. Please.</i>

42:57.324 --> 42:58.492
<i>I got it. We're good.</i>

42:58.576 --> 43:01.912
<i>-Sure?
- Yeah. Just watch the front.</i>

43:03.664 --> 43:06.500
<i>Nothing to see here.
Keep it moving.</i>

43:06.584 --> 43:08.252
<i>It's all good.</i>

43:09.837 --> 43:13.924
<i>P-Please, don't. Please, please.
Please, don't hit me. Please.</i>

43:14.633 --> 43:15.718
<i>Hey.</i>

43:15.759 --> 43:17.720
<i>Hey, I'm not gonna do that.</i>

43:17.761 --> 43:20.472
<i>It's okay. Hey.</i>

43:20.556 --> 43:23.100
<i>Please, don't hit me. Please.</i>

43:48.208 --> 43:51.295
<i>-Hi.
- Hello.</i>

43:58.761 --> 44:00.512
<i>Oh.</i>

44:00.596 --> 44:01.722
<i>You okay?</i>

44:01.805 --> 44:03.390
<i>Every single time.</i>

44:03.432 --> 44:05.392
<i>Right?</i>

44:05.476 --> 44:06.477
<i>My name's Lee.</i>

44:06.518 --> 44:08.896
<i>-You're new.
- Hopefully.</i>

44:08.979 --> 44:10.773
<i>I'm waiting to be interviewed.</i>

44:10.856 --> 44:13.817
<i>Rachel. Good luck.</i>

44:25.621 --> 44:26.664
<i>Who are you?</i>

44:26.705 --> 44:28.332
<i>Lee.</i>

44:28.374 --> 44:30.876
<i>No. I recognize you.</i>

44:30.918 --> 44:32.378
<i>You were
at Billy Poe's arraignment.</i>

44:32.419 --> 44:34.755
<i>You were crying.
What are you doing here?</i>

44:34.838 --> 44:37.508
<i>I'm taking
a few months off law school</i>

44:37.591 --> 44:38.884
<i>to be with my family,</i>

44:38.926 --> 44:40.803
<i>and I wanted to find a place
where I could help.</i>

44:40.844 --> 44:42.554
<i>There are lots of places
where you can help.</i>

44:42.596 --> 44:44.181
<i>Legal Aid. Pittsburgh ACLU.</i>

44:44.264 --> 44:45.808
<i>I was impressed
by your work in the courtroom.</i>

44:45.849 --> 44:48.018
<i>You came here
expecting to work with me?</i>

44:48.060 --> 44:50.270
<i>-I was hoping to.
- On this case?</i>

44:50.312 --> 44:51.563
<i>If you need it.</i>

44:51.605 --> 44:52.815
<i>I don't need it.</i>

44:52.856 --> 44:54.817
<i>I don't need your help, period.</i>

44:54.900 --> 44:56.694
<i>You stay away from me,
we'll be all right.</i>

44:56.735 --> 44:58.987
<i>I think you do need it.</i>

44:59.446 --> 45:03.617
<i>Billy's probably
stonewalling you, right?</i>

45:03.659 --> 45:06.078
<i>He's gonna keep doing that.</i>

45:06.161 --> 45:08.205
<i>If he ever does see you,
it'll be too late</i>

45:08.247 --> 45:09.873
<i>for you to help him.</i>

45:10.666 --> 45:13.043
<i>I can get you in to talk to him.</i>

45:13.627 --> 45:15.796
<i>How do you know that?</i>

45:15.879 --> 45:18.882
<i>Because he's in love with me.</i>

45:48.746 --> 45:51.665
Some people wondering
where you were today.

45:51.707 --> 45:55.252
<i>Yeah. Not feeling so great.</i>

46:03.343 --> 46:05.304
<i>-It's high.</i>

46:05.345 --> 46:07.264
<i>Huh.</i>

46:09.266 --> 46:14.605
<i>Well, maybe that's just 'cause
you're sitting so close to me.</i>

46:18.108 --> 46:19.985
<i>Look, I know how tired you are.</i>

46:20.068 --> 46:21.653
<i>Why don't you
just stay here tonight.</i>

46:21.695 --> 46:23.697
<i>That way I can just take it
again in a couple hours.</i>

46:23.739 --> 46:26.700
<i>No, you...
You don't have to do that.</i>

46:26.742 --> 46:28.786
<i>You don't have to do
any of this.</i>

46:28.827 --> 46:30.788
<i>Yes, I know I don't.</i>

46:30.871 --> 46:33.290
<i>I want to.</i>

46:34.082 --> 46:37.920
<i>Everything's happening
at the same time.</i>

46:38.504 --> 46:41.632
<i>That poor kid died last night.</i>

46:42.466 --> 46:43.801
<i>I think I might be close</i>

46:43.884 --> 46:46.804
<i>to finding the guy
who named Billy.</i>

46:46.887 --> 46:48.555
<i>He could be connected</i>

46:48.639 --> 46:52.643
<i>to all the drugs
around the community.</i>

46:53.519 --> 46:56.313
<i>Trying to be a good cop.</i>

46:59.650 --> 47:03.320
<i>The guy who named Billy
is a drug dealer?</i>

47:04.404 --> 47:06.323
<i>I think so.</i>

47:06.824 --> 47:09.368
<i>Hard drugs?</i>

47:09.409 --> 47:10.994
<i>Uh-huh.</i>

47:11.036 --> 47:13.288
<i>quiet, dramatic music</i>

47:16.500 --> 47:19.002
<i>Can you prove it?</i>

47:20.546 --> 47:23.340
<i>Not yet.</i>

47:24.508 --> 47:27.344
<i>But I'm trying.</i>

47:31.515 --> 47:34.017
<i>I know you are.</i>

47:35.143 --> 47:37.062
<i>Don't worry.
You'll figure it out.</i>

47:37.104 --> 47:39.690
<i>We're in this together.</i>

47:42.818 --> 47:45.696
<i>Just let me take care of you.</i>

47:49.032 --> 47:52.703
<i>You do your work,
and I'll watch out for you.</i>

48:09.636 --> 48:11.513
<i>ominous, dramatic music</i>

48:31.033 --> 48:31.992
<i>Get in there!</i>

48:32.075 --> 48:34.703
<i>Bring him in!</i>

49:06.234 --> 49:09.237
<i>Get up!
Get up, motherfucker!</i>

49:09.821 --> 49:11.782
<i>Come on! Come on!</i>

49:18.664 --> 49:20.123
<i>Come on!</i>

49:27.089 --> 49:29.091
<i>Fucking go!</i>

49:31.259 --> 49:34.930
<i>That's right, baby.
Hands up. Hands up!</i>

49:35.013 --> 49:35.847
<i>Let's go!</i>

49:35.931 --> 49:38.058
<i>Beat the shit out of him!</i>

49:38.141 --> 49:40.519
<i>Beat the shit
out of him!</i>

49:48.777 --> 49:51.196
<i>Come on. Get up.</i>

49:51.863 --> 49:53.865
<i>Come on!</i>

49:53.907 --> 49:57.035
<i>-Get up!</i>

49:57.119 --> 49:59.121
<i>intense, dramatic music</i>

50:00.080 --> 50:03.208
<i></i>

50:21.018 --> 50:22.310
<i>Get him, man!</i>

50:22.352 --> 50:24.521
<i>-Get him, man!
- Kill him!</i>

50:24.604 --> 50:26.648
<i>Kill him!
Fuck him up!</i>

50:26.690 --> 50:28.692
<i>Yeah! Yeah!</i>

50:30.777 --> 50:31.945
<i>Yeah!</i>

50:32.029 --> 50:34.281
<i>-Kill him!
- Do it!</i>

50:34.322 --> 50:37.117
<i>All right!
All right, that's it!</i>

50:37.159 --> 50:40.370
<i>Get him up. Come on. Get up.</i>

50:44.166 --> 50:46.877
<i>Told you! Told you!</i>

50:48.086 --> 50:50.672
<i>-Get him out of here.</i>

50:53.341 --> 50:56.511
Go to your bunks.
It's past your bedtime.

50:57.137 --> 50:59.598
<i>Jesus.</i>

51:16.990 --> 51:20.702
<i>quiet, dramatic music</i>

51:38.261 --> 51:40.597
<i>You did good.</i>

52:09.751 --> 52:11.962
<i>Sleep well.</i>
